{
  "stem": "7093.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so anyway, I eventually-- Ilan, and Ilan was incredibly bright.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was brilliant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And at 17, he got to university.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it-- and at 26, he became a-- he became professor at Zurich University as a geneticist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he would have-- this year, he would have had the Nobel Prize, because two people with whom-- who started working on his project got the Nobel Prize.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But anyway, at the age of 30, he committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And before that, he had, at the age of 21, he had an-- his first affair with a young woman who was older than he was and who-- and there, there is a child from that relationship, which lasted three weeks.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "After three weeks, he didn't want to go out with her anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then she came that she's pregnant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She said she was on the pill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then there is a son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was the son whom my son never want to see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I-- from the beginning on, I was grandmother for-- granny to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I'm still granny to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He's now in Oxford and is doing his doctorate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I hope so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He's very, very bright.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he has a master's degree.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he's 24-- has a, has a degree and a master's degrees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he's doing now his doctorate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then he married a French girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he became-- and he had a-- and he had a daughter in '77, and in '79-- whom he absolutely adored.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But his wife hated Zurich and left with the child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because she just couldn't get accustomed to Zurich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He was a workaholic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He had little time for her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And she went back to Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And, and in '79, he committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
